                            A <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Palindrome">palindrome</a> is a word, phrase, number, or other sequence that reads the same backword or forward.
                            <br />Example:
                        </p>
                        <pre class="examp">Hannah</pre>
                        <p>Enter a word, phrase, or number and click the button to see if it's a palindrome.</p>
                        <input type="text" id="testPal" class="form-control input-sm col-xs-1" /><br /><br />
