                            A <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Perfect_number">Perfect number</a> is a positive integer that is equal to the sum of its 
                            proper positive divisors (all positive divisors excluding the number itself).
                        
                            <br />Example:</p>
                        </p>
                        <pre class="examp">1 + 2 + 3 = 6</pre>
                        <p>Enter a positive integer and click the button to see if it's a Perfect Number.</p>
